Package: reactablePlus
Title: Enhanced Interactive Tables with Inline Editors for Shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Matthew", "Currier", email = "first.last@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Extends 'reactable' with inline editing widgets (pickers,
    popovers, text inputs) and a declarative configuration layer for
    building editable tables in Shiny applications. Provides a generic
    editable table module driven by row and column specifications, plus
    a library of cell-level input widgets with custom Shiny bindings.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/matthewcurrier/reactablePlus,
    https://matthewcurrier.github.io/reactablePlus/
BugReports: https://github.com/matthewcurrier/reactablePlus/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
